  %method
    %signature width="VALUE"
    %p Set width of widget. VALUE may include a units suffix, which overrides the inherited units.
    %p A leading - (minus sign) or + (plus sign) makes the value relative to the container's width.
    %p A trailing % (percent sign) makes the width a percentage of the parent's width.

